body:
Welcome to my second Nebula challenge!
Here's the first one, if you haven't done it yet: http://avicus.net/forums/53f8b1ca0
Challenge #2
"The F5 Challenge"
In this challenge, you must get an objective in Nebula DTM using F5 mode!
It is the first F5, the one where you press F5 once.
This one: http://imgur.com/spJvIMq
There aren't really any rules, just play a normal game, get an objective, but in F5 mode.
Good luck!
~DiamondPorkchop3
